				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				A large sewing kit is unbelievably better than a small one. This is what I know can be made in a Large Sewing Kit:  Raw Silk Tunic, Raw Silk Leggings.  (Check EVERLORES GUIDE TO TAILORING for the reasons and alot of information on tailoring) Actaully there are a ton more but all for the same reason: Items that require more than 2 components (Which is basically everything in mid to high level tailoring skill) need the extra slots within the large sewing kit.  In a small one, there are only two slots thus if something requires three comoponents or more...your screwed untill you can get the large kit :) (Get the large kits as soon as possible (buy at auction if you have to) if you are going to be a tailor.  They are totally necessary for advancing in that skill and they hold big things like halberds that backpacks cant; and they have 8 slots just like a pack! PLUS they have A large sewing kit is unbelievably better than a small one.  This is what I know can be made in a Large Sewing Kit:  Raw Silk Tunic, Raw Silk Leggings.  (Check EVERLORES GUIDE TO TAILORING for the reasons and alot of information on tailoring) Actaully there are a ton more but all for the same reason: Items that require more than 2 components (Which is basically everything in mid to high level tailoring skill) need the extra slots within the large sewing kit.  In a small one, there are only two slots thus if something requires three comoponents or more...your screwed untill you can get the large kit :) (Get the large kits as soon as possible (buy at auction if you have to) if you are going to be a tailor.  They are totally necessary for advancing in that skill and they hold big things like halberds that backpacks cant; and they have 8 slots just like a pack! PLUS they have A large sewing kit is unbelievably better than a small one.  This is what I know can be made in a Large Sewing Kit:  Raw Silk Tunic, Raw Silk Leggings.  (Check EVERLORES GUIDE TO TAILORING for the reasons and alot of informatio